metadata.name: KENSEI #1
metadata.description:
Kensei (剣聖) aka Sword saint is a Japanese honorary title given to a warrior of legendary skill in swordsmanship.

"Stay away from me"

The first character from a series of illustrations Japanese warriors made by Artem Over.

The owner of the NFT is entitled to a high-quality poster on A3 or A2 archival paper or the original file for self-printing if it is not possible to send a physical poster by mail. Please, [contact] (https://telegram.me/artemover) me after the end of the auction
